Southern California R Users Group

Welcome to the Southern California R Users Group (SoCal RUG)! Since no single group can serve this sprawling area, several RUGs from Santa Barbara to San Diego joined forces to centralize SoCal-based R events and information.

In addition to our core SoCal RUG team, our archive includes events hosted by our extended R alliance including the following groups: R-Ladies Irvine, R-Ladies Los Angeles, R-Ladies Pasadena, R-Ladies Riverside, R-Ladies Santa Barbara, R-Ladies San Diego, Santa Barbara RUG, and San Luis Obispo RUG.
